Metadata-Version: 2.3
Name: openwebpos
Version: 0.1.0.dev1
Summary: OpenWebPOS is an open-source, web-based Point of Sale (POS) system designed for restaurants and mobile food vendors. Built with Python and Flask, it provides a user-friendly, responsive interface powered by MaterialiceCSS and HTMX. OpenWebPOS offers features like product management, order tracking, and user authentication, making it a reliable, scalable, and customizable solution for small businesses.
